725952f-a.title: Queens: 164th Street - 89th Avenue
725952f-a.text:
164th Street, adjoining the S. W. corner of 89th Avenue,
showing the First Church of Christ, Scientist.
April 1,1932
P. L. Sperr

725953f-a.title: Queens: 164th Street - 89th Avenue
725953f-a.text:
82-48 164th Street, west side, between 89th and Jamaica
Avenues, showing an old dwelling. Note the ornamentation.
The house on the right is an old mansion influenced by
Norman architecture.
P. L. Sperr  April 1, 1932
